post.description:
The user status filter is for registry version only. 


User Status: Active=1, Inactive=0, All=-1

Sample request for Registry Version:
            
    POST /api/Agency/GetContacts
    {
       "userStatus": 1,
       "paging": {
          "pageSize": 20,
          "pageIndex": 0
       }
    }
            
Sample request for Non-Registry Version:
            
    POST /api/Agency/GetContacts
    {
       "paging": {
          "pageSize": 20,
          "pageIndex": 0
       }
    }

